reviewText: In this collection you get to see Hawaii like you're there in real time, seeing more than what a tour guide would show. You get an all access pass to this vacation destination and you can see the Boos (from the great World of Boo book series) too! This is a must see for any fan of paradise. Looking forward to future Maddy Venture films of Hawaii.
A daily journey with the filmmaker as he explores and adventures across his adopted island home of Oahu. A great way to discover the lesser travelled sections of the 50th state.
